title: [SOLVED]820-3435-B Fan spin, no cpuvcore
message:
820-3435-B, corrosion damage to u7600 area, r7630 blown and replaced, computer now gets fan spin, however no cpu vcore, and pp1v05 is 0.4v, replaced u7600, checked r7611 and r7612.
Replaced  q7630 and l7630. pp1v05 remains 0.4v.

I'm lost, have checked every component in the 1.05v s0 regulator circuit, feel like I'm missing something obvious.
